main event: A GOC observer spotted a round object the size of a pin head while on duty in the operations room.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 30 seconds.,The sighting coincided with the presence of a jet aircraft in the area.,The observer kept the object in sight until it was lost near the location of the approach.,No reports are found in the file regarding this event.,The object was classified as an air visual observation.
sighted object: one round object the size of a pin head
witness description: GOC observer on duty in the operations room
